# **1.Executive Summary**

**Overview:**  
This project is a graphical implementation of the classic Hangman game using C++ and the SFML library. It allows users to guess a randomly selected word with the help of a hint feature, visually rendering the hangman figure as guesses are made.

**Key Findings:**  
The project successfully demonstrates core concepts of Object-Oriented Programming and graphics handling through SFML. It has modular design, real-time input handling, and a user-friendly interface.
